e="preserve">"America's Next Top Model, Cycle 16" is the sixteenth cycle of "America's Next Top Model" and the tenth season to be aired on The CW network. It premiered on February 23, 2011. The international destination for this cycle is Marrakech, Morocco. The winner was 19-year-old Brittani Kline from Beech Creek, Pennsylvania.
